</P>
<P>
   That's what we have to say,
</P>
<P>
   Your grades need a new complexion, even if it scares you to stay
awake.
</P>
<P>
   Oh, oh oh what's ``tired'' got to do, got to do with it?
</P>
<P>
   What's ``tired,'' but a second-hand emotion?
