<SLUG> BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX </SLUG>
 
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Fort Worth Star-Telegram plans to move the following stories
for clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of
Thursday, June 29, and thereafter. If you have any questions,
please call Carmelita Bevill, Lou Hudson or Jim Peipert on the
Star-Telegram's National/Foreign Desk at (817) 390-7785. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Visit the Star-Telegram's online services on the World Wide
Web: www.star-telegram.com) &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
