<HEADLINE>
THE FORGOTTEN IRELAND
</HEADLINE>
  Hospitality beckons from the Dingle Peninsula 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Fact box and captions below. Art available.) 
By GLENN WHIPP 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
