<P>
   BOOKS-POTTER (Undated) _ Security guards. Slumber parties.
Lightning-bolts. Threats. They're all part of the fever building to
July 8 when ``Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire,'' the latest in
the madly popular Harry Potter series of children's books, goes on
sale.
